#Time series line
transactions1 %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_line(aes(x=date,y=amount))+
  labs(title = "Time series plot of the highest number of transactions account") +
  xlab("Date") +
  ylab("Amount")

#time series with credit and debit
transactions1 %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_line(aes(x=date,y=amount))+
  facet_wrap(~type)+
  labs(title = "Time series plot of the highest number of transactions account with type") +
  xlab("Date") +
  ylab("Amount")

#time series with different method
transactions1 %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_line(aes(x=date,y=amount))+
  facet_wrap(~method)+
  labs(title = "Time series plot of the highest number of transactions account with method") +
  xlab("Date") +
  ylab("Amount")

#time series with different categories
transactions1 %>%
  ggplot()+
  geom_line(aes(x=date,y=amount))+
  facet_wrap(~category)+
  labs(title = "Time series plot of the highest number of transactions account with category") +
  xlab("Date") +
  ylab("Amount")
